Hello.

My name is Liam Turner.

Through the decades I've collected this set of archived websites to act as a microcosm of what happened to our world; a brief glimpse into the madness of the past century.

I don't know the people who created them, beyond the fact that they are, in all likelihood, dead.

Let this be a lesson to anyone who tries to replicate what was done here.
